collapse\n |title=NFC Divisional Round: #6 New Orleans Saints at #1 Seattle Seahawks&nbsp;\u2013 Game summary\n |date=January 11, 2014\n |time=3:35 p.m. CST/1:35 p.m. [[Pacific Time Zone|PST]]\n |road=Saints\n |R1=0|R2=0|R3=0|R4=15\n |home='''Seahawks'''\n |H1=6|H2=10|H3=0|H4=7\n |stadium=[[CenturyLink Field]], [[Seattle, Washington]]\n |attendance=68,388\n |weather={{convert|48|F|C}}, rain\n |referee=[[Terry McAulay]]\n |TV=[[NFL on Fox|Fox]]\n |TVAnnouncers=[[Kevin Burkhardt]], [[John Lynch (American football)|John Lynch]] and [[Erin Andrews]]\n |reference=[http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2014011100/2013/POST19/saints@seahawks Recap], [http://www.nfl.com/liveupdate/gamecenter/56162/SEA_Gamebook.pdf Game book]\n |scoring=\n'''First quarter'''\n*SEA \u2013 [[Steven Hauschka]] 38-yard field goal, 10:19. ''Seahawks 3\u20130. '''Drive: 6 plays, 20 yards, 3:20.'''''\n*SEA \u2013 Steven Hauschka 49-yard field goal, 0:37. ''Seahawks 6\u20130. '''Drive: 9 plays, 34 yards, 4:26.'''''\n'''Second quarter'''\n*SEA \u2013 [[Marshawn Lynch]] 15-yard run (Steven Hauschka kick), 14:17. ''Seahawks 13\u20130. '''Drive: 2 plays, 24 yards, 0:34.'''''\n*SEA \u2013 Steven Hauschka 26-yard field goal, 1:18. ''Seahawks 16\u20130. '''Drive: 12 plays, 63 yards, 4:44.'''''\n'''Third quarter'''\n*No scoring plays\n'''Fourth quarter'''\n*NO \u2013 [[Khiry Robinson]] 1-yard run ([[Mark Ingram Jr.|Mark Ingram]] run), 13:11. ''Seahawks 16\u20138. '''Drive: 9 plays, 74 yards, 4:27.'''''\n*SEA \u2013 Marshawn Lynch 31-yard run (Steven Hauschka kick), 2:40. ''Seahawks 23\u20138. '''Drive: 4 plays, 62 yards, 1:11.'''''\n*NO \u2013 [[Marques Colston]] 9-yard pass from [[Drew Brees]] ([[Shayne Graham]] kick), 0:26. ''Seahawks 23\u201315. '''Drive: 9 plays, 80 yards, 2:14.'''''\n |stats=\n'''Top passers'''\n*NO \u2013 [[Drew Brees]] \u2013 24/43, 309 yards, 1 TD\n*SEA \u2013 [[Russell Wilson]] \u2013 9/18, 103 yards\n'''Top rushers'''\n*NO \u2013 [[Khiry Robinson]] \u2013 13 rushes, 57 yards, 1 TD\n*SEA \